: green;\">Normal</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Potassium</td><td>4.2</td><td>mmol/L</td><td style=\"color: green;\">Normal</td></tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n                <button style=\"margin-top: 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 10px 15px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer;\">View Full Report</button>\n            </div>\n        </aap:section>\n\n        <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20px;\">\n            <!-- Third Column/Wide Area: Medications -->\n            <div class=\"data-panel\" id=\"meds\" style=\"flex: 1 1 30%;\">\n                <h2>Active Medications</h2>\n                <ul style=\"list-style-type: none; padding: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eee; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                        <strong>Lisinopril</strong> <span style=\"float: right; color: #007bff;\">10mg</span>\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 0.9em; margin: 5px 0 0;\">Take 1 tablet daily in the morning.</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eee; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                        <strong>Metformin</strong> <span style=\"float: right; color: #007bff;\">500mg</span>\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 0.9em; margin: 5px 0 0;\">Take 2 tablets twice daily with meals.</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eee; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 4px; background-color: #fff3cd;\">\n                        <strong>Vitamin D</strong> <span style=\"float: right; color: #007bff;\">1000 IU</span>\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 0.9em; margin: 5px 0 0;\">Take 1 capsule daily.</p>\n                    </li>\n                </ul>\n                <p style=\"margin-top: 20px;\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #dc3545;\">[Review Medication List]</a></p>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Fourth Column/Wide Area: Encounter Notes -->\n            <div class=\"data-panel\" id=\"encounter\" style=\"flex: 1 1 40%;\">\n                <h2>Latest Physician Notes</h2>\n                <p><strong>Provider:</strong> Dr. Angela Ramirez, MD</p>\n                <p><strong>Date:</strong> 2024-07-21</p>\n                <h4 style=\"margin-top: 15px;\">Summary:</h4>\n                <p style=\"font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                    Patient stable in the telemetry unit following minor GI upset. Vitals remain within acceptable parameters. \n                    Continue current regimen of antihypertensives and continue cardiac monitoring per protocol. \n                    Follow-up required with Cardiology in two weeks. Diet consultation recommended.\n                </p>\n                <h4 style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">Plan:</h4>\n                <ol style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n                    <li>Continue current medications.</li>\n                    <li>Monitor electrolytes closely.</li>\n                    <li>Physical therapy scheduled for tomorrow morning.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n    </div>\n\n    <aap:section id=\"footer\">\n        <div id=\"footer\">\n            <small>&copy; 2024 HealthConnect Dashboard. For informational purposes only. Data accurate as of today's session.</small>\n        </div>\n    </aap:section>\n\n</body>\n</html>","bindings":{"str_0":"UTF-8","str_1":"viewport","str_2":"patient-name","str_3":"dashboard-container","str_4":"nav","num_5":"333","num_6":"08","num_7":"600"}}]}
